    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep luster and no chips, scratches, or dings of any kind. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, featuring pristine upholstery and surfaces that show zero signs of wear. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that is truly indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent care and mechanical integrity. This unit offers a refined driving experience, characterized by dependable performance and a well-preserved interior. Thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for safety and operational excellence, it stands as a premier choice for the discerning driver seeking lasting value and sophistication. Experience a vehicle that balances proven longevity with a commanding road presence.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road? I\u2019m parting with my car and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in wonderful condition, runs super smoothly, and has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, so you can drive away with total peace of mind. It's perfect for daily commutes or your next big road trip\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains composed with documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. Mechanical longevity is ensured via a recent VANOS service and precision valve adjustment. Equipped with the M Variable Differential Lock for superior lateral dynamics, this example balances raw performance with consistent maintenance. A purist-spec machine ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Minor exterior scuffs. Interior well-kept. Mechanically sound. Service records available.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a brilliant shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper tell the story of its road experience. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is free of tears or stains, and all electronic features\u2014including the navigation, premium sound system, and dual-zone climate control\u2014function precisely as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and a fresh oil service. The engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. It sits on a set of tires with plenty of tread remaining and features clean alloy wheels. With a complete folder of service records and a clean title in hand, this is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, this model offers a balanced synthesis of performance and long-term value. Every component has been thoroughly vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for daily reliability and road-going excellence. Secure a sophisticated driving experience that prioritizes both quality and value.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s still got so much life left in her! It\u2019s been a fantastic ride for me\u2014super reliable and handles like a dream. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-maintained, perfect for someone looking for a dependable daily driver without breaking the bank. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home where it'll be appreciated as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the legendary S65 naturally aspirated V8 platform. The 4.0L engine delivers linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline, with the double-VANOS system ensuring optimal torque across the rev range. This unit features the desirable 6-speed manual gearbox, providing a direct mechanical connection to the rear-mounted M Variable Differential. Recent service includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, addressing key preventative maintenance items. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), maintaining excellent damping characteristics and lateral stability. While the exterior shows minor road wear typical of a driven classic, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance remain robust.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
